  "description": "A breathtaking vista of a coastal sunset over a city and bay. The sky is ablaze with vibrant orange and red hues, streaked with wispy, elongated clouds. The clouds are a mix of deep orange near the horizon, transitioning to lighter shades of pink and yellow higher up. Below the dramatic sky, a calm bay stretches towards the distant hills. A city is nestled along the shoreline, with visible buildings and infrastructure. In the foreground, silhouetted vegetation, predominantly shrubs and trees, forms a dark, textured border. The scene conveys a sense of tranquility and grandeur.",
